{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回 患难见真情\n\n马如龙与大婉被困于一条深巷之中，七名黑衣蒙面人前后夹击。马如龙欲让大婉独自逃生，大婉却指出这些黑衣人并非为捉拿凶手而来，而是冲着她来的。两人互相推让，谁也不肯抛下对方独自逃走。马如龙以\"我做不出这种事\"为由坚持留下，大婉虽嘴上说他笨，心中却因他的义气而感动。\n\n黑衣人首领手持龙凤金环，冷冷逼近。大婉巧言周旋，暗示马如龙会拼命护她，逼得黑衣人承认要动她必先杀马如龙。此时一个看似平凡的卖花女出现，大婉见之色变，竟施展惊人轻功飞身越墙逃走。卖花女更以穿墙神功破壁而去，令众人震惊。\n\n黑衣人转向马如龙，声称利剑出鞘必须见血。马如龙拼死搏斗，先击倒身材高大的黑霸，又以铁牌击退金环、判官笔等围攻。然而跨虎篮配合金环攻势奇诡，马如龙渐感力不从心。危急时刻，邱凤城银枪突至，以\"要杀他先折断这杆枪\"的豪言加入战团。二人联手，枪拳并用，杀退天杀杀手。\n\n战后，邱凤城握住马如龙的手，温暖地说他实在需要喝杯酒。患难之中，友情愈见真挚。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你用不着害怕，我会叫他们放你走的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他们会让我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "这件事根本和你完全没有关系，为什么不让你走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你认为，他们是来找你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "当然是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你错了。我也希望他们是来找你的，可惜不是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "为什么不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是个凶手，来捉拿凶手，不但光明正大，而且是很露脸的事，为什么要把脸用黑布蒙起来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是你也用不着害怕，我也会叫他们放你走的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你认为我会走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们非亲非故，别人来要我的命，难道你也要陪我一起死？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我总不会把你一个人留在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因我做不出这种事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这理由不够好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可是对我来说，已经足够了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "说不定我是个坏女人，是个贼，你本应该帮他们把我抓住才对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我知道，你绝不是这种人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怎么知道，你连我究竟姓什么都不知道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可是我相信你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我本来以为你已经变得聪明了些，想不到你还是这么笨。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "喂，你们是来找我的？还是来找他的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "是来找你的又怎么样？是来找他的又怎么样？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "如果是来找他的，就没有我的事了，我既不是英雄也不是君子，你们就算杀了他我也绝不管你们的闲事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你不必说，我也看得出。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "可是你们如果是来找我的，情况就不同了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "他自己的麻烦虽然已经够多，还是不肯像我一样袖手旁观的，你们只要动一动我，他就会跟你们拼命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "所以我们若是要动你，就一定要先杀了他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是不是这样子的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "喂，你们听见他说的话没有？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "看来他不但是个英雄，还是个君子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "看来他的确是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "只可惜这种人总是不长命的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "这句话我早就告诉过他了，可惜他偏偏不听。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怕不怕？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你怕，现在要走也许还来得及。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我不走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那么我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我要走了，你不走，我走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你们要找的是她？还是我？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "她已经走了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "对你来说，很不好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duo_ming_jin_huan",
      "speaker_name": "手提龙凤双环的黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为你应该知道，利剑出鞘，不能不见血，否则必定不祥。我们这些人也一样，只要我们出手，就非杀人不可，现在她已走了，我们只有杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_ba",
      "speaker_name": "黑霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀了他！杀了他！杀！杀！杀！杀！杀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_huan_jin_huan_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你们要杀他，就得先折断这杆枪，你们要折断这杆枪，就得先杀了我！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我看得出你现在需要什么？你现在实在需要喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "温柔",
